Troubleshooting Tips
ffuf not finding any paths:

Verify web server is running: sudo systemctl status nginx
Check wordlist file exists and is readable
Test manually: curl http://localhost/admin
Python script connection errors:

Ensure target URL includes http:// or https://
Check firewall settings: sudo ufw status
Verify network connectivity: ping localhost
High false positive rate:

Use response size filtering: -fs flag in ffuf
Filter common 404 page sizes
Analyze response content, not just status codes
